divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside this last May around dusk and looked over to the west in the lower sky was a white light low in the sky. As I was watching it, it seemed to change shape and turn a red & orange color as it was slowly going down tell I could no longer see it.
Summary: Observed white light in lower sky at dusk for about an hour slowly going down then turn red & orange tell it droped down out of sight.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Phoenix
This sighting has never been favorited.
